scribing\n\n### Tool Compatibility\nThe service is compatible with mainstream AI coding tools including:\n- QwenCode\n- ClaudeCode  \n- Cline\n- Other AI development tools\n\n### Pricing Plans\nAccording to the search results, there are two subscription tiers:\n\n**International Market:**\n- **Lite version**: $10/month\n- **Pro version**: $50/month\n\n**Chinese Market:**\n- Lite basic version available with special pricing for new users (starting from 7.9 RMB for first month)\n\n## Related Context\n- On **February 16, 2026** (Chinese New Year's Eve), Alibaba also open-sourced the new **Qwen 3.5** large language model\n- The Coding Plan launch follows the release of Qwen2.5-Max version which was released on Chinese New Year 2025\n\nThis represents Alibaba's expansion into the AI programming services market, offering competitive pricing for both domestic and international developers.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
